###

GET {{DocumentApi_HostAddress}}/api/workslips?limit=25&offset=0
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{DocumentApi_HostAddress}}/api/workslips/{{ReportId}}
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{DocumentApi_HostAddress}}/api/document-types/{{DocumentTypeId}}/view-model
Accept: application/json

###

